<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/22819894">军事游戏中有哪些有悖实际之处？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1308693" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">原问题：军事游戏中有哪些常见的谬误？<br>包括各种fps，当然，快被打死了站一会儿就好了这种大家都懂的。</div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
<div class="zm-meta-panel">

